&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Thermal camera macro</title><link>https://kittenlabs.de/thermal-macro-adapter/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kittenlabs.de/thermal-macro-adapter/</guid><description>&lt;img src="featured-8b75dd6d-f493-413d-9426-ec7b0068ed7c.jpg" width="60%" alt="Thermal camera, with a macro lens attached">
&lt;h2 id="what-is-it">What is it?&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#what-is-it" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>3D-printable adapter, which fits into commercial thermal cameras and adds a 18mm ZnSe CO2 laser lens to the optical path.&lt;br>
This greatly improves the imaging quality on small electronics / SMD parts.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="before--after">Before / After&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#before--after" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
