The microcontroller is an ATmega2560 (Arduino Mega-compatible), chosen for 5V-I/O voltage and high pin-count (and bad availability of STM32&amp;rsquo;s in the component shortage of 2021).&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>TCP/IP for Casio calculators</title><link>https://kittenlabs.de/fxip/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Jul 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kittenlabs.de/fxip/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="menu.jpeg" width="49%" alt="Casio calculator menu, with fxIP app"> &lt;img src="featured-webserver.jpeg" width="49%" alt="Casio calculators, showing fxIP start screen">&lt;/p>
